{"tid":863841,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大埔仔返柴灣ive的辛酸","createTime":"2018-10-16T01:01:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-16T03:43:33.000Z","uid":213225,"like":26,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"8f997fca5c751555b995805cbc9a9ebf07e22cf1","tid":863841,"uid":213225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T01:01:21.000Z","msg":"今日港鐵又跪低 <br />\n全世界都企L左喺到<br />\n每條線都話要等半個鐘先轉到<br />\n我要轉3次線 搭到我懷疑人生<br />\n然後阿sir咁大gp話體諒大家<br />\n叫我地去票務處拎証書。。<br />\n嘩 我當堂嚇左一跳 然後得啖笑<br />\n我已經喺站頭排隊排到灰<br />\n你仲叫我要拎証書？<br />\n好 有人真係要問人拎証書<br />\n港鐵話未準備好 問阿sir可以點。。<br />\n佢就冇再回覆了 唉 就算我幾勤力<br />\n每日早3個鐘返學 我永遠都唔會有100%出席率<br />\n依加我連7成嘅出席率都擔心緊<br />\n到底我要幾早出門先可以順利返學？🙁"},{"pid":"b62c10e86857e77bcaaafc3467367da149adf741","tid":863841,"uid":42448,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T01:06:13.000Z","msg":"識唔識搭118P？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65ef05fb22c07e3772289d03ea5b71367d3f1e30","tid":863841,"uid":15921,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T01:08:09.000Z","msg":"紅隧轉車好難？"},{"pid":"fadc92c0e6ccd0cf30dbac642a2aacb2708b7533","tid":863841,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T01:09:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f2aaf8f8dca1b4ec1caa4cf726b33a32cffcd75","tid":863841,"uid":213225,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"65ef05fb22c07e3772289d03ea5b71367d3f1e30","tid":863841,"uid":15921,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T01:08:09.000Z","msg":"紅隧轉車好難？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T01:13:07.000Z","msg":"港鐵有事 紅隧會順咩🤷🏼&zwj;♂️"},{"pid":"04d0ee634f69208699367513b5215c50e2d874a6","tid